column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.fiberMag_g, p.fiberMag_r, p.fiberMag_i, p.fiberMagErr_g, p.fiberMagErr_r, p.fiberMagErr_i, i.specObjID, i.subclass FROM galSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON p.objID = s.bestobjid JOIN galSpecInfo AS i ON i.specObjID = g.specObjID WHERE s.zWarning=#&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
